        "subject": "LU-14300 tests: run testing on OST pools patch",
        "message": "LU-14300 tests: run testing on OST pools patch\n\nWe are trying to determine what patch is causing sanity-sec\ntest 18 to hang.  Let's try and reproduce the hang on a\nversion of Lustre that HEAD is the OST pool quota patch.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nTest-Parameters: fstype=zfs mdtcount=1 mdscount=1 env=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes testlist=sanity-sec,sanity-sec,sanity-sec\nTest-Parameters: fstype=zfs mdtcount=1 mdscount=1 env=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes,ONLY=18,ONLY_REPEAT=50 testlist=sanity-sec\nTest-Parameters: fstype=zfs mdtcount=1 mdscount=1 testgroup=full\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <jnunez@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Id57cc67dcc49dbc2eb5eb92ec398d382395f6b68\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
